    "author_channel_id": "UC5nQynPt1hiHtk9QXxKqXuQ",
    "text": "Handy tip I discovered from YouTube, Prusa slicer  has a slicer feature that can automatically place dowels or pegs, and even dovetails, saves a lot of guess work and/or beer mat calculations/tolerance experimentation, ideal for certain prints for all sorts of reasons, multitasking jobs over machines or to save needless waste on support material.",
