    "author_channel_id": "UC8ImAgPG5qDLmpgf2LJLTFA",
    "text": "Hello Robbert.\nHave you ever considered how a compressor refrigerator device would work in combination with a peltier electric generator.  If a refrigerant compressor circuit gives 4kw of energy for every 1kw of energy put in, the peltier device only needs to exceed 25% efficency before it starts making energy from warm air.  I know these devices have low efficency but combined with a refrigerant it may increase. I did see that a patent had been applied for a few years ago regarding a refrigerant thermoelectric generator. Hope you explore this in a video. I'd like to see the results.",
    "likes": 2,
    "published_at": "2023-10-26T18:38:57Z",
    "reply_count": 1,
    "replies": [
